 Daarnaast kunnen zij best practices opstellen en helpen bij het implementeren van de nieuwste Teams-innovaties. Met hun kennis kunnen onze consultants op directieniveau meedenken en adviseren over de juiste Teams implementatie. ","Sugar Glaze",false,{"id":198,"name":199,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":200,"height":201,"formats":202,"hash":229,"ext":23,"mime":206,"size":230,"url":231,"previewUrl":18,"provider":54,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":232,"updatedAt":232,"documentId":233,"publishedAt":57,"focalPoint":18},782,"Teams.jpg",1280,850,{"large":203,"small":210,"medium":216,"thumbnail":222},{"ext":23,"url":204,"hash":205,"mime":206,"name":207,"path":18,"size":208,"width":29,"height":209},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","large_Teams_43eca91eed","image/jpeg","large_Teams.jpg",75.76,664,{"ext":23,"url":211,"hash":212,"mime":206,"name":213,"path":18,"size":214,"width":36,"height":215},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","small_Teams_43eca91eed","small_Teams.jpg",24.28,332,{"ext":23,"url":217,"hash":218,"mime":206,"name":219,"path":18,"size":220,"width":43,"height":221},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","medium_Teams_43eca91eed","medium_Teams.jpg",45.38,498,{"ext":23,"url":223,"hash":224,"mime":206,"name":225,"path":18,"size":226,"width":227,"height":228},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","thumbnail_Teams_43eca91eed","thumbnail_Teams.jpg",8.28,235,156,"Teams_43eca91eed",119.1,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","2024-08-08T09:42:56.910Z","ht6rctym4qbbspr1vnahyrg1","global.alternating-page-section",{"id":236,"title":237,"subTitle":238,"content":239,"callToActionText":240,"callToActionLink":162,"colorStyle":241,"showAsides":196,"imageUrl":242,"__component":234},28,"Adoptie","Adoptie van Microsoft 365 diensten","Het aanschaffen van een programma of pakket kan iedereen. Maar ervoor zorgen dat je medewerkers optimaal gebruik maken van de mogelijkheden die Microsoft biedt, is een ander verhaal. Onze experts zorgen ervoor dat jouw medewerkers methodisch leren werken met Microsoft 365 programma’s. Deze methode, de adoptiestraat, is al bij vele ShareValue-klanten met groot succes uitgevoerd. Wordt jouw organisatie de volgende?","Meer weten over de ShareValue adoptiestraat?","White",{"id":243,"name":244,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":200,"height":201,"formats":245,"hash":266,"ext":23,"mime":206,"size":267,"url":268,"previewUrl":18,"provider":54,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":269,"updatedAt":269,"documentId":270,"publishedAt":57,"focalPoint":18},783,"adoptie.jpg",{"large":246,"small":251,"medium":256,"thumbnail":261},{"ext":23,"url":247,"hash":248,"mime":206,"name":249,"path":18,"size":250,"width":29,"height":209},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","large_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","large_adoptie.jpg",140.54,{"ext":23,"url":252,"hash":253,"mime":206,"name":254,"path":18,"size":255,"width":36,"height":215},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","small_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","small_adoptie.jpg",46.09,{"ext":23,"url":257,"hash":258,"mime":206,"name":259,"path":18,"size":260,"width":43,"height":221},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","medium_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","medium_adoptie.jpg",90.06,{"ext":23,"url":262,"hash":263,"mime":206,"name":264,"path":18,"size":265,"width":227,"height":228},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","thumbnail_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","thumbnail_adoptie.jpg",13.08,"adoptie_dc3bbcacaa",204.86,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","2024-08-08T09:47:03.256Z","kqdvjnnutm27pjz49n0b8l8r",{"id":272,"title":273,"subTitle":274,"content